casebody.data:
Suzanne RUBBA and Daniel LeBlanc, Personal Representatives for the Estate of Patricia E. LeBlanc, Plaintiffs-Appellees,
v.
Eugene J. AGNONE, M.D., Chakrpani Ranganathan, M.D., Michigan Cancer Specialists, PLC, and Macomb Neurology Associates, PC, Defendants,
and
Michael F. Romanelli, M.D., and Woods Cardiovascular Internal Medicine Associates, PC, Defendants-Appellants. SC: 156319
COA: 330416 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 28, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the July 6, 2017 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.

Viviano, J., did not participate due to a familial relationship with the presiding circuit court judge in this case.
